ote":{"pid":"f91de9f6ef77292d231a46c518356f2919479ec6","tid":2098513,"uid":303571,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"而家先知係實名制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔撚投算 反正都係幫泛民做球"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:36:18.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n唔好一黎就話唔撚投<br />\n睇定D先<br />\n睇下民動會唔會走出黎回應"},{"pid":"011f3d9d001a54711ecb01ab3c02bad1ea24bdd8","tid":2098513,"uid":17506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65c26e9f7428337ec7746d1776fef6c4409177b7","tid":2098513,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"可以用紙張投票"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:36:22.000Z","msg":"🏢邊度投？<br />\n全港設251個「服務點」供市民電子投票，<span style=\"color: red;\">亦有少量票站設紙張投票。</span><br />\n票站名單（持續更新）：<a href=\"https://qrgo.page.link/uVuQi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqrgo.page.link%2FuVuQi&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=ae73bdd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qrgo.page.link/uVuQi</a><br />\n票站 Google Map: <a href=\"https://is.gd/DndK3B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FDndK3B&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=ef538fe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/DndK3B</a><br />\n🗳點投票？<br />\n1. 安裝初選投票 app 《普及投票 4.0》<br />\n-- Andriod版: <a href=\"https://is.gd/tH1bbk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FtH1bbk&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=8164ff80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/tH1bbk</a><br />\n-- iOS版: 有待公佈<br />\n2. 進入app, 順序填入以下資料<br />\n(i) 職員提供的票站編號<br />\n(ii) 是否傳統功能組別的選民<br />\n(iii) 身分證後四位數字（不包括號內數字）<br />\n(iv) 身分證簽發日期<br />\n(v) 出生日子（僅日子, 無須月份或年份）<br />\n3. 係app揀完候選人之後，會得到一個QR code<br />\n4. 拎埋身份證同選民身份證明去到投票地點<br />\n5. 向投票地點工作人員展示身分證，以供驗證<br />\n6. 向投票地點工作人員提供以下任何一份文件：<br />\n(i) 住址證明; 或<br />\n(ii) 官方選舉選民通知書; 或<br />\n(iii) 電子版選民查冊截圖 <a href=\"htt