否傳統功能組別的選民<br />\n(iii) 身分證後四位數字（不包括號內數字）<br />\n(iv) 身分證簽發日期<br />\n(v) 出生日子（僅日子, 無須月份或年份）<br />\n3. 係app揀完候選人之後，會得到一個QR code<br />\n4. 拎埋身份證同選民身份證明去到投票地點<br />\n5. 向投票地點工作人員展示身分證，以供驗證<br />\n6. 向投票地點工作人員提供以下任何一份文件：<br />\n(i) 住址證明; 或<br />\n(ii) 官方選舉選民通知書; 或<br />\n(iii) 電子版選民查冊截圖 <a href=\"https://is.gd/kUFN66\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FkUFN66&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=4d5e7a42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/kUFN66</a><br />\n7. 俾職員核實QR code就完成投票！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103001221140027/photos/a.103940267712789/280080830098731/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103001221140027%2Fphotos%2Fa.103940267712789%2F280080830098731%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=53e8d462\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103001221140027/photos/a.103940267712789/280080830098731/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n未必有得用紙張投票,但唔洗比全名同全部身分證號碼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:41:17.000Z","msg":"岩岩見佢呢個留言, 我搵左資料<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3238052129613718/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3238052129613718%2F&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=31f305b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3238052129613718/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfyNTnm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfyNTnm.png&h=6d2345e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最底果行細字 係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">後備方案</span></strong><br />\n簡單D黎講應該即係紙票唔會好多<br />\n用哂就無<br />\n<br />\n同埋手機投票要打個人資料用黎validate張票<br />\n佢都無講到用紙張呢個後備方案洗唔洗寫個人資料先validate到張票"},{"pid":"3f6e5ca0ff74eddd41495acb32a883061c976f40","tid":2098513,"uid":99391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"qu